Nemesis + Blade route

Start
	Get Polar Star
	Item Quit in Shack
		Activate Balrog Cutscene, >NO
	Exit, go to Cemetery + Arthur's Key
	collect Map System
	PROBABLY pick up life capsule in arthur's house
	Save in Arthur's House, Exit

The Bushlands Shuffle
	Time Attack, Item Quit
	Load file, Map System, open Santa's sign for Nemesis, interact santa's key for BOOSTER 2.0 and ARMS BARRIER
	interact sign near malco's door for BLADE
	save at right save point
	reload
	OPTIONAL but EXTREMELY recommended: item quit in execution chamber, interact the lower right frog for health, save, reload
	bushlands save point, save, item quit bushlands, door, save in arthur's house

Ballos
	item quit in Mimiga Village Save Point, inventory teleport to bushlands, breakdown to plantation
	enter hideout, leave storeroom, enter passage, enter statue room, item quit
	inventory teleport to bushlands, enter santa's house
	kill ballos